    "The nature of the integration of humans and technologies in organisations is a messy one which requires careful consideration of how decisionmaking occurs and by what regulatory framework it is guided.",
    "To get a sense of the issues, two case studies are referred to here.",
    "Without a careful review of the decision-making of governance, GAI and the algorithmic culture they belong to have been shown to have problematic outcomes for equity in policing.",
